Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you sell cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't carry them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, back there? \NBy the tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was performing a ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... sorry I intruded then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, do you know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still spiraling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a dark, lonely feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought maybe you could rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow, I still feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm moved by the scent of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for those smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The simple act of pursuing her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having reached an impasse\Nin my work and in myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sought to acquaint myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with everyday ennui,\Nsired by apathy and restlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever-fleeing the authenticity\Nof my own experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was entirely spent by a life, \Ncomposed of accumulated fictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,are you always alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not be alone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know today's date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you perform your ritual today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It will make my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When my wish comes true,\NI can disappear completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappear, leaving nothing\Nin the world behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to keep\Nperforming the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, the red umbrella protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what's tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you follow me,\Nthat first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you following me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... because you intrigue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My unsound heart
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the consuming loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of longing for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps anyone will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as that someone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will love me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}constantly, ceaselessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Is this true love?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I feel at ease with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"We're compatible."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ponder such ideas everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad and Mom are sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everybody's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sickest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's stood there before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I felt strange. {I merged this and the last line into one sentence in my previous version, but I am not so sure about that anymore. Thoughts?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You look just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only my favorite things are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Including me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of the gang. {Going to need the eldon TLC on this one. JP -> IT -> EN is certainly a pipeline}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I like coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, your sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She never listened to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for regrets now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, \Nor you'll end up like your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you share that man's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!\NWhere are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with that man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up the phone and call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked myself\Nto the bone to raise you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At least your sister had a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if you keep up this selfish behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You, you, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you talk to me that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father tortured me,\Ndoing whatever he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And now my own daughter {line break?}hates me this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of living...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get out of the hospital tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's your birthday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please? Won't you come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NSo let's play together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone\Non my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainy days are days\Nfor my father and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow's my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No doubt for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the truth is only an enemy that wounds her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days of her life pass in\Nloneliness, a darkness without exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I longed to ease her sadness\Nand anxiety, if only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if only to atone\Nfor my own past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I be with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,5:59 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,30 seconds. {tbh i'd prob just put these all together unless there's a reason it shuld be split like this}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,5:59 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,5:59 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,50 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,6 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,6 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,give you a tour of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,First,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret fourth floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,first floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absolutely secret!\NYou can't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,fifth floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,sixth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,seventh floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they all secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These... stairs...\NI'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting old...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You like high places?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I come here to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Check what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The light is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,everything's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's better if I didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How about my blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I'm still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Still okay to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A blank-faced mosquito falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge mosquito,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,much, much bigger than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It slumps and is still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A much larger creature caught it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and took flight, the mosquito in its grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew up and passed right over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it released its grasp\N and the mosquito fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Still blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It drifted down, down, down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The inside of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an interesting head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to talk. {TLC / TODO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Something, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything. I want to hear you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know FireMan? {I've seen people capitalize it like this but I feel like "Fireman" would be more correct no?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he was like UltraMan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His enemies attack him\Nand in the end, he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He ignites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,FireMan ends up burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He yells "Fire!" but\Nactually he's afraid of fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's FireMan 'cause he burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it,\Nbut it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what she says,\Nbut I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, all she wanted was\Nto hear someone's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, all she wanted was\Nto stop feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Echoes from the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}creaking arcade roof opening\Nand an all too ordinary sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}disturbed my ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see you tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You like cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as much as boats and trains,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:22:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I like 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my big sister did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was back at the hotel\Ngetting my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean where\Nwere you 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I took my usual route here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the bookstore, department store,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the toy store today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean where were you\Nbefore you came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I wanted to think things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was kind of tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:24:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.63,0:24:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, it was all about nothing. {TODO}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother always said\Nlife is full of tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.30,0:24:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No phone calls today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the deal's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.21,0:24:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:24:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.81,0:25:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My usual work exhausts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.71,0:25:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm keeping my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanted to\Nmake live action films, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.64,0:25:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Live action films... films.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.89,0:25:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Films?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.48,0:25:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Films...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.28,0:25:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's stopping you? You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.78,0:25:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you're "Director".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.46,0:25:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.71,0:25:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.85,0:25:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.97,0:25:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.79,0:25:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want blue, the blue one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.72,0:25:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This? This blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.81,0:25:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.27,0:25:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.21,0:25:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.93,0:25:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.97,0:25:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.96,0:26:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.20,0:26:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?\NTomorrow's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.88,0:26:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.44,0:26:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.20,0:26:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still okay today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.96,0:26:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.44,0:27:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I start shooting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.00,0:27:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.38,0:27:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.95,0:27:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An outline by...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.94,0:27:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Reel 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.89,0:27:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.23,0:27:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.03,0:27:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shooting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.98,0:27:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.78,0:27:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.73,0:28:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my outfit look alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.09,0:28:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.97,0:28:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I think it looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.56,0:28:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about clothes. {alt: costumes}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.33,0:28:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.99,0:28:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.71,0:28:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you shooting...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.43,0:28:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.23,0:28:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.98,0:28:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.66,0:29:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy on the train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.46,0:29:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.93,0:29:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.08,0:29:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.49,0:29:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The streetcar is a perfect means of escape \Nfrom the tedium of my days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.56,0:29:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scenery flows by cinematically.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.66,0:29:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sound effects are punctual. {TODO: Retime}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.66,0:29:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My fantasy about her expands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.00,0:29:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be bored for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.34,0:29:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our idle routine, the days \NI spend with her, like a lukewarm bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.65,0:29:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}her faint smile seems to agree with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.38,0:29:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each day, a countdown towards death.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.05,0:29:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dare not risk negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.91,0:29:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the more reason to film her, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.74,0:29:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Images, especially animation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.30,0:29:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}simply embody our\Npersonal and collective fantasies,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.40,0:30:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}manipulating selected information,\Nand fictional constructs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.33,0:30:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in live-action film, \Nrecording actuality, does not correspond to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.93,0:30:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Conversely, reality, \Nco-opted by fiction, loses its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.07,0:30:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The inversion of reality and fiction."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.36,0:30:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}None of this matters to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.87,0:30:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My consciousness, my reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.99,0:30:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my subject, all converge in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly, she longs to escape into fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.08,0:30:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly, I long to escape from fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.12,0:30:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to keep a visual record\Nof these contradictory phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.66,0:30:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, my behavior is really\Nno more than an excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.33,0:30:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for my inability to communicate\Nexcept through images.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.64,0:30:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way to the mystery basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.49,0:31:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No trespassing\Nbecause the camera is prohibited,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.02,0:31:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot show you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.98,0:31:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies {TODO: Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.28,0:31:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.64,0:31:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,force me to omit the first \Nthrough seventh floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.59,0:31:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.88,0:31:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.64,0:31:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's high...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.37,0:31:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where she always checks herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.43,0:31:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.10,0:31:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.03,0:31:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each day, she postpones tomorrow,\Nby transforming today into yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.42,0:32:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A typical day in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never goes to sleep before dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.07,0:32:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she awakens before 6 AM\Nto dial and listen to the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.33,0:32:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As far as I can tell,\Nshe hardly sleeps at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.28,0:32:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.67,0:32:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.74,0:32:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.41,0:32:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to sleep? {TODO: Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.47,0:32:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.23,0:32:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I close my eyes to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.08,0:32:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,something really heavy \Nseems to crush my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.63,0:32:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I push it away and away and away,\Nbut it keeps bearing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.58,0:32:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't avert my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.61,0:33:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.99,0:33:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.13,0:33:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like tomorrow coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.89,0:33:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.93,0:33:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.20,0:33:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.12,0:33:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Terrified to face the truth,\Nshe rejects even sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.66,0:33:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that there is actual truth\N in the ambiguity of human memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.20,0:33:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her best and only means\Nof survival depends on her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.95,0:33:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destruction and renewal of memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.39,0:33:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly many more days bear\Nforgetting than joyful commemoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.94,0:33:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it that I want from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.42,0:33:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're shooting again tomorrow... {TODO: Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.50,0:34:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again, today, I record her image.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.16,0:34:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I find in the act\Nof capturing her being,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.23,0:34:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}according to my own will, \Nfor my own purpose, relief from my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.23,0:34:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Images transform my real past into fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.78,0:34:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each of us edits and alters our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.66,0:34:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By giving form and existence\Nto this process through images,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.71,0:34:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I reinvent my past, whitewashing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.50,0:34:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}into an idealized history.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.65,0:34:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Re-creating the present as something invulnerable,\N as a world of fiction and fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.02,0:34:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are the same, only differing in our methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.70,0:34:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.40,0:35:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.84,0:35:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you read this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.60,0:35:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.73,0:35:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.93,0:35:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.13,0:35:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.84,0:35:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.57,0:35:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I read the softer stuff. {Folded under ZERO pressure}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.98,0:35:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do read it. Disgusting. {Split} {would probably keep this together for CPS since the next line starts so early. that or you have an ugly overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.17,0:35:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Playboy, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.88,0:35:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Females drowning in their lust,\Ncoming wherever they please..."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.55,0:35:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.42,0:35:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Normal sex doesn't do it"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.09,0:35:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.05,0:35:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"The nymphomaniacs who lust for kinky settings"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.46,0:35:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{}Cut it out. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.87,0:35:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.71,0:35:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.28,0:35:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You like this stuff too. {boob} {Should this be a question mark?}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.18,0:36:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.18,0:36:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, "vavoom".
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.03,0:36:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.96,0:36:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.80,0:36:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.75,0:36:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You do like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.66,0:36:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.65,0:36:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all men like sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.66,0:36:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.26,0:36:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Director \Nneither likes nor dislikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.96,0:36:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't dislike it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.76,0:36:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.10,0:36:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.91,0:36:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause if you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no more\Nthan male and female.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.87,0:36:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.33,0:36:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.65,0:37:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.91,0:37:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kumoha 42 street car.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.65,0:37:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The type: \N20 meters with driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.21,0:37:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Two doors and benches on either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.71,0:37:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Semi-cross seats\Nperpendicular to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.17,0:37:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Street car color: \NGrape #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.43,0:37:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Capacity of 104,\N68 sitting, 36 standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.85,0:37:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Weight: 45 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.35,0:37:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Built in 1933. {Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.86,0:37:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These two cars are the only ones\Nof this type still operating in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.64,0:37:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.00,0:37:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.64,0:37:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in Ube.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.49,0:37:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.03,0:37:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell whether it's any good or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.75,0:38:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll email you an outline when I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.87,0:38:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.64,0:38:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds good. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.43,0:38:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from a woman again, Dirty Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.99,0:38:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.64,0:38:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.22,0:38:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At least once a day\Nyou get to talk to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.73,0:38:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.64,0:38:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who it is.\NAt least someone calls you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.48,0:38:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.68,0:38:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.25,0:38:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.22,0:39:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That night,\Nher smile disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.74,0:39:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with the falling rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.38,0:39:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.36,0:39:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.52,0:39:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.66,0:40:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.80,0:40:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.58,0:40:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.72,0:40:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.48,0:41:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.54,0:41:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.22,0:42:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.62,0:42:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,my father and sister's day!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.86,0:42:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I like rainy days,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.73,0:42:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because when it rains,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.95,0:42:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,all the merry people in the world\Nfinally walk with their eyes downcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.37,0:42:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I like rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.27,0:42:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rain she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.53,0:42:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What she keeps bottled up on sunny days,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.40,0:42:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}flows as from a broken darn when it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.56,0:42:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her feelings of loneliness and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.19,0:42:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These emotions elevate her,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.92,0:42:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}preventing her from \Nengaging in a certain behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.36,0:42:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.59,0:42:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}engendering her complex reactions\Nto the phenomenon called rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.79,0:42:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the sadness that she harbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.76,0:43:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No doubt the deaths in her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.26,0:43:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this moment, I acknowledge yet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.22,0:43:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that in her heart, she yearns
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.58,0:43:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to cease existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.32,0:43:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A brand new morning's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.11,0:43:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A morning of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.87,0:43:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your heart with joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.66,0:43:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up at the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.54,0:43:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your vibrant heart
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.27,0:43:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to the song on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.30,0:43:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fragrant breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.55,0:43:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, 1, 2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.59,0:43:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.77,0:43:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Having something to hold onto\Nwhen you're scared
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.06,0:43:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is good enough in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.95,0:44:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.57,0:44:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,secret
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.11,0:44:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ritual space.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.73,0:44:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It always has to be flooded. \NIt's a really sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.99,0:44:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But as of today, it's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.22,0:44:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Director can come and go.\NVideocamera okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.82,0:44:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.33,0:44:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.86,0:44:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,An umbrella here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.64,0:44:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.07,0:44:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.46,0:44:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.34,0:44:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.41,0:44:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A videocamera.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.22,0:44:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Matching.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.74,0:44:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.12,0:45:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A hesitant reply isn't a good sign, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.43,0:45:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.45,0:45:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A favorite place?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.71,0:45:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Favorite place...\NThis sort of place isn't bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.17,0:45:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.86,0:45:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.24,0:45:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.87,0:45:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple place with only sand and sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.42,0:45:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.77,0:45:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was beautiful\Nbecause it was unpopulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.37,0:45:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No humans there to warp it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.77,0:45:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful world\Nwithout people.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.41,0:45:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.16,0:45:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like railroad tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.24,0:45:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.48,0:45:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.31,0:45:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.63,0:45:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How shall I put it...\NBecause they are mechanical.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.47,0:46:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then rails are fixed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.19,0:46:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you ride them,\Nyou needn't choose a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.24,0:46:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.67,0:46:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.30,0:46:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.59,0:46:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.04,0:46:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these two rails
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.61,0:46:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,will never come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.95,0:46:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.73,0:46:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the two are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.09,0:46:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.21,0:46:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.85,0:46:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abused and then abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.46,0:46:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.61,0:46:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my fear made me tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.60,0:46:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The magical powers\Nof a pair of dice
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.58,0:46:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}still sway me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.32,0:46:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}undiminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.28,0:46:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only one day I could say
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.61,0:46:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.28,0:46:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hum to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.45,0:47:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My umbrella!\NMy umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.86,0:47:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I died in your place... {ngl I just followed the original timing for the most part cause this scene is a clusterfuck -aigis}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.16,0:47:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the skies part?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.97,0:47:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the wind flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.50,0:47:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beneath the steps of that dark red space
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.08,0:47:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you used that sharp stick
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.79,0:48:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and struck my bursting...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.37,0:48:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.45,0:48:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, I can't write.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.96,0:48:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.34,0:48:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe time to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.96,0:48:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do if I quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.53,0:48:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.73,0:48:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.63,0:48:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.88,0:49:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, she didn't\Nventure near the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.55,0:49:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or to the railroad tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.71,0:49:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never attempted\Nto leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.29,0:50:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.29,0:50:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.54,0:50:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.27,0:50:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.07,0:50:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never discussed what frightened her,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.11,0:50:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what she wanted to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.99,0:50:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She no longer saw anyone but herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.51,0:50:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer exist inside of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.49,0:50:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day passed without us\Nexchanging a single word,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.37,0:51:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a single glance, \Nor lifting the camera to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.08,0:51:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For I hadn't the courage\Nto capture her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.69,0:51:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her unrelenting, oppressive reality
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.80,0:51:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}began to bear down on me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.77,0:51:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbeknownst to me, \Nshe had found a cat that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.43,0:51:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look mother,\Nisn't this cat cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.45,0:51:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.82,0:51:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's mother, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.43,0:51:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our very, very kind mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.38,0:51:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say hello to her, Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.95,0:52:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.49,0:52:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.88,0:52:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.38,0:52:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her ritual remained interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.09,0:52:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since that day, she hadn't climbed\Nto the roof, or visited the tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.37,0:52:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but played with the cat all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.13,0:52:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Playing with the cat seemed to\Nallow her to avoid herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.57,0:52:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She still slept rarely,\Nand now barely ate,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.94,0:52:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}only played with the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.74,0:52:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing else worth\Nrecording took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.56,0:52:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Except that of course we neither\Nspoke nor exchanged a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.01,0:52:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remained locked outside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.56,0:52:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Jam!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.57,0:52:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.25,0:53:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat slipped away that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.38,0:53:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The photographer's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.63,0:53:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The writer's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.13,0:53:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The director's obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.84,0:53:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The actor's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.92,0:53:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Red cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.65,0:53:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Swelling lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.56,0:53:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tightened strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.53,0:53:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human heart is fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.64,0:53:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and is easily captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.20,0:53:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An evil song,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.79,0:53:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}drifting through the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.06,0:53:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}envelopes the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.03,0:53:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.01,0:53:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Announcing,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.76,0:53:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My true mother has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.21,0:53:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girl dances
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.76,0:54:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wildly, wildly
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.36,0:54:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wildly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.61,0:54:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never did come home that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.05,0:55:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.43,0:55:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I noticed that I was somewhat\Nrelieved the cat had gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.19,0:55:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.88,0:55:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.77,0:55:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.48,0:55:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.02,0:56:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.86,0:56:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.46,0:56:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.58,0:57:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.93,0:57:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.89,0:57:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why weren't you\Nwith me then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.41,0:57:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.09,0:57:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.33,0:57:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.98,0:58:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.48,0:58:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beating away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.70,0:58:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A gentle sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.96,0:58:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.57,0:59:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.91,0:59:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disappear like that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.63,0:59:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever leave me alone again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.79,0:59:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.86,0:59:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.06,0:59:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.01,0:59:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.78,1:00:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with me on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.93,1:00:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.83,1:00:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.88,1:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.15,1:00:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.44,1:01:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.91,1:01:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, wake up!\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.92,1:01:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's past 6!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.32,1:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No... hold on...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.21,1:01:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.54,1:01:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.29,1:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.88,1:02:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.62,1:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart says I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.93,1:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There there...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.22,1:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Which line today?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.05,1:02:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.03,1:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.33,1:03:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's someone scary!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.48,1:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Director! Monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.37,1:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkeys and goats!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.52,1:03:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a huge discovery this morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.98,1:03:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.42,1:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared to fall asleep anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.15,1:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you were with me,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.13,1:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I could close my eyes just like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.29,1:03:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And like,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.06,1:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.04,1:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing came crashing down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.43,1:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, my body felt really light.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.31,1:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.30,1:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.39,1:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really amazing!\NDo you understand what this means?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.95,1:04:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing discovery!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.54,1:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.43,1:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Great angle.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.02,1:04:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's not so bad when I lie like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.17,1:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.27,1:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuddling is nice, isn't it? I like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.21,1:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.92,1:05:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, I like this better
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.26,1:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.23,1:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.36,1:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.22,1:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, well then,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.45,1:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you like about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.97,1:05:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.81,1:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.40,1:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.37,1:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when I wake up in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.93,1:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you're beside me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.07,1:05:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.73,1:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.42,1:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn't it? {Split maybe?}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.06,1:05:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.39,1:05:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But your mouth's
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.68,1:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,always wide open, and you drool.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.21,1:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You... fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.71,1:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.76,1:05:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it over?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.73,1:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All these used tires
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.72,1:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,look like people's ripped off teeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.87,1:06:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me shoot too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.33,1:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? I want to shoot, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.63,1:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it won't be my film anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.83,1:06:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.73,1:06:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me, let me!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.31,1:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This okay? Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.18,1:06:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.43,1:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.70,1:06:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.63,1:06:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you upset?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.34,1:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.14,1:06:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.20,1:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.93,1:06:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look upset?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.32,1:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You do!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.15,1:06:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.59,1:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.84,1:06:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been tired lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.44,1:06:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tired?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.44,1:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.25,1:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.34,1:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to baby you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.77,1:07:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.21,1:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good boy, good boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.41,1:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll baby you more.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.49,1:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you mother me then?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.52,1:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a piggyback.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.64,1:07:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Piggyback?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.42,1:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, piggyback.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.62,1:07:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.38,1:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A two-shot!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.98,1:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dizzy!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.50,1:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.54,1:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.16,1:08:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.31,1:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.49,1:08:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.11,1:08:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.70,1:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.28,1:08:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.91,1:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's nearly a month since I met her.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.75,1:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fed up with the endless "yesterdays",
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.00,1:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and lulled by the "todays."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.42,1:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anxious, too, that tomorrow may bring change,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.53,1:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet eagerly awaiting the change it may finally bring.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.35,1:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I want from this reality I share with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.60,1:10:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The constancy of the past or the change of the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.69,1:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.11,1:10:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these were no more than idle doubts that shifted with my moods.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.24,1:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You snore every night, just like a hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.64,1:10:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These days will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.31,1:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I'll part with her. {Split}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.84,1:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even my life will end one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.27,1:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the more reason to treasure\Nthese slight, fleeting emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.18,1:10:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the excess of boredom and intimacy
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.69,1:10:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}were simply exhausting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.66,1:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I realized that gradually,\Nthe times that being with her depressed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.04,1:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}outstripped the times that I enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.19,1:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday that'll happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.31,1:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, today,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.83,1:11:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there was this blue car
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.38,1:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of the shrine,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.25,1:11:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and this car, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.75,1:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was really cute...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.08,1:12:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you listening?\NYou paying attention?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.23,1:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.45,1:12:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.17,1:12:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to the store.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.13,1:12:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He hates me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.87,1:12:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.03,1:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He hates me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.16,1:12:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hates me, hates me, hates me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.30,1:12:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be left alone again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.18,1:12:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be left alone again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.73,1:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.87,1:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abused and then abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.06,1:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried everything
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.26,1:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my fear made me tremble.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.02,1:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The magical powers of a pair of dice...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.24,1:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...still sway me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.60,1:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only one day I could say,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.96,1:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'm so glad I met you."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.78,1:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hum to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.30,1:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, your sister...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.54,1:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.21,1:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She never listened to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.79,1:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for regrets now!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.94,1:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, or you'll\Nend up like your sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.89,1:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you share\Nthat man's blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.14,1:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.39,1:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.67,1:14:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with that man again!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.66,1:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.49,1:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, clueless!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.20,1:14:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so patronizing!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.52,1:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All you ever want is\Nfor me to be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.31,1:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Always, always, always.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.89,1:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just patronizing me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.68,1:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have a clue
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.68,1:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is I really want! Not a clue!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.26,1:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.48,1:14:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You only remember what you gave me,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.34,1:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but not how you mistreated me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.58,1:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.40,1:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what, we're even for all your troubles?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.02,1:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and die!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.67,1:14:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,\NI won't care! {Split}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.98,1:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.60,1:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you nice to me then?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.88,1:15:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.12,1:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.73,1:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.50,1:15:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer? {added these repetition lines cause I think 4 is fine without it being obnoxious like the "tomorrows my birthday" spam earlier -aigis}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.73,1:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.99,1:16:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her heart is overcome by a world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.08,1:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}awash in cruelty, harshness,\Nhatred and loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.60,1:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that is the way of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.79,1:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each of us fears its absurdity, and curses it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.62,1:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, the world is immeasurably vast,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.87,1:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and gentleness, mercy and\Nempathy linger in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.66,1:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I desperately wanted her\N to know this reality as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.60,1:16:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.55,1:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.60,1:16:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{this is sus but im not seeing anything else you'd time this to -aigis}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.47,1:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But her heart is so delicate and vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.10,1:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I really capable of embracing
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.58,1:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the endless darkness inside it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.35,1:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I'm incapable of accepting her...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.37,1:17:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I find myself enveloped\Nin an anxiety I cannot shake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.11,1:17:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, again, I can do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.78,1:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}6 in the morning,\Nshe's back to her usual self
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.81,1:17:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's returned to her little world
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.10,1:17:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}constructed entirely
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.62,1:17:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of her protections, denying the existence
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.96,1:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of whatever can harm her.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.32,1:17:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Except now she has chosen to rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.92,1:17:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it always sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.22,1:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She begins another day of life,\Nbrimming with fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.94,1:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}plastered in self-deception,\Nsealed by oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.24,1:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My own faint panic,\N"I've got to do something"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.64,1:18:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is futilely idle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.68,1:18:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.65,1:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, just working.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.20,1:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside then.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.02,1:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot your movie,\Nthat's your job, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.90,1:18:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that work?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.26,1:18:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.47,1:18:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Japan today, all forms of expression,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.87,1:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}beginning with images, serve only
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.32,1:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as either
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.49,1:18:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}time-killing entertainment\Nfor those without occupation,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.17,1:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or as momentary respite \Nfor those who are afraid of pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.02,1:18:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People desire either real scandals\Namplified by rawness,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.92,1:18:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.22,1:18:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the illusion of beautifully adapted fictions.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.46,1:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is true of me. {What does this mean??? | probably means "i'm no different" -aigis}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.29,1:19:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unable to create appropriate relationships,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.90,1:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I escape into a fictional world,\Nconstructed on a fantasy of daily life.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.95,1:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even this film, when completed,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.18,1:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will become a device to deliver\Na certain amount of pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.44,1:19:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Devoid of surprises,\Nand a measure of time spent in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.67,1:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who wants images beyond that?\NWho needs them?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.10,1:19:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By then, I had abandoned\Nher as a visual construct.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.64,1:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't want to film anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.88,1:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as she was present,\NI didn't need to make a film.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.98,1:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had always been entranced with the idea of
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.14,1:19:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}being madly loved, and loving madly.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.46,1:19:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet this was a stupendous burden, exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.70,1:19:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could I really bear it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.40,1:20:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.62,1:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came back!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.95,1:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.13,1:20:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! 
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.19,1:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.56,1:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.85,1:20:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.67,1:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.46,1:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.92,1:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.98,1:20:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back,\NI know you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.51,1:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You do, right!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.23,1:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not my sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.62,1:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.81,1:21:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.78,1:22:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.35,1:22:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.40,1:22:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.32,1:22:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A reunion? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.88,1:22:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A toast to his triumphant return!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.55,1:22:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.65,1:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.90,1:25:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.57,1:26:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.62,1:26:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.72,1:26:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With some woman?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.90,1:26:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.28,1:26:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out drinking\Nwith my old friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.04,1:26:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar, liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.87,1:26:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.79,1:26:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.05,1:26:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.89,1:26:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.04,1:26:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying. It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.86,1:26:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.55,1:26:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but your heartbeat.
Comment: 0,1:26:56.55,1:26:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{should prob be something here, like a "say" or whatever -aigis}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.33,1:27:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever kissed someone?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.48,1:27:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.52,1:27:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I haven't ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.69,1:27:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever killed someone?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.43,1:27:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.13,1:27:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. {could prob extend this with like "Actually... maybe I have." or something cause just "maybe" for the whole line feels like it's missing something -aigis}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.45,1:27:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.93,1:27:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.12,1:28:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to have sex?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.98,1:28:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have sex with you,\Nwill you stay forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.73,1:28:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.87,1:28:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Much better than cuddling.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.83,1:28:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You just put up with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.62,1:28:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see \Nand touch my breasts, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.15,1:28:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, have sex with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.52,1:28:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.99,1:28:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.53,1:28:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.98,1:28:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.32,1:28:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start hating me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.21,1:29:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.50,1:29:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.89,1:29:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do this,\NI will become my sister...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.12,1:29:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become my sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.10,1:29:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm... Still... {again, mostly followed what officials had cause the overlapping voices are just a pita -aigis}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.14,1:29:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I died in your place.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.42,1:29:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the skies part.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.11,1:29:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the wind flow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.76,1:29:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beneath the steps of that dark red space
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.27,1:29:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you used that sharpened stick
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.08,1:30:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.12,1:30:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}striking my
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.57,1:30:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}quivering lips
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.52,1:30:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}swollen to bursting
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.18,1:30:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tasting
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.63,1:30:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of sorrow and betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.13,1:30:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That song
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.62,1:30:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.27,1:30:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I peer back again and again
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.22,1:30:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at that dreamlike state.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.33,1:30:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.\NSorry, I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.13,1:31:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.72,1:31:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How unusual. Calling at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.90,1:31:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat got your tongue?\NHello, hello...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.22,1:31:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.69,1:31:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.61,1:32:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You read this?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.66,1:32:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.22,1:32:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.20,1:32:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.52,1:32:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.70,1:32:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you have to?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.52,1:32:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with me because\Nyou have to be for work?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.16,1:32:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.53,1:32:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my father?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.32,1:32:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.49,1:32:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.75,1:32:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.76,1:32:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I worthless?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.88,1:32:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.10,1:32:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going away?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.02,1:33:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.78,1:33:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.99,1:33:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.86,1:33:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just tempted when \Nshe called you, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.94,1:33:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What woman?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.02,1:33:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's nobody...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.74,1:33:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Irrelevant...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.67,1:33:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.54,1:33:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear your heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.24,1:33:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.00,1:33:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Two answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.88,1:34:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Three answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.05,1:34:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How many answers?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.26,1:34:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you like this...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.23,1:34:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By 6 that morning, she had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.88,1:34:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of my sister's?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.51,1:34:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You dating her?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.40,1:34:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.58,1:34:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... That girl got a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.23,1:34:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.04,1:34:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought she'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.38,1:35:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her sister appeared instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.22,1:35:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, she'd rejected even herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.04,1:35:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of my business,\Nbut be nice to her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.98,1:35:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \Nshe always liked this kind of place.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.84,1:35:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.39,1:35:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our parents split up \Nwhen she was young,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.82,1:35:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father walked out on both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.95,1:35:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wound up dead with the new woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.37,1:35:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it rain on that day?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.48,1:35:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, went ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.58,1:35:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.92,1:35:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.09,1:35:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And, your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.52,1:35:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A streetcar hit her.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.29,1:35:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,On her birthday, she'd always cry,\N"Why did they leave me?"
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.08,1:35:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mother was a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.51,1:36:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She blamed anything bad on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.30,1:36:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Dad's fault,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.57,1:36:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that woman's fault,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.64,1:36:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,my sister's fault, my fault,\Nthe world's fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.20,1:36:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It never occurred to her\Nthe fault might be hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.63,1:36:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.06,1:36:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always compared to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.99,1:36:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She only heard nagging, \N"Why can't you be like your sister?"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.93,1:36:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like she was no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.68,1:36:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have suffered.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.11,1:36:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how she'll\Never learn to like herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.87,1:36:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone I'd like to see. You coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.84,1:37:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business, butt out.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.78,1:37:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.94,1:37:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,New guy, huh...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.00,1:37:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Must run in the family.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.63,1:37:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.48,1:37:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You only show up when it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.12,1:37:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that face?\NSame as last time?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.87,1:37:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seen my cat?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.47,1:37:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.02,1:38:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My cat, my cat,\Nyou know, Jam.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.14,1:38:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.48,1:38:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell would I know?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.27,1:38:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar, liar, liar, liar...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.74,1:38:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You deny attacking my little sister, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.38,1:38:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou are her, not her sister. {???}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.59,1:38:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.43,1:38:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister went away a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.57,1:38:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You ranted about killing her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.67,1:38:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I say I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.85,1:38:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were babbling some crap\Nabout how you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.04,1:38:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.43,1:38:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You do this to me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.42,1:38:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask me to let you stay\N'cause you got nowhere else,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.99,1:38:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then you split.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.58,1:38:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's about some cat!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.79,1:38:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You come wandering back\Nranting about a cat!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.07,1:39:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.68,1:39:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.46,1:39:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.00,1:39:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After all I did for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.58,1:39:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.13,1:39:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.86,1:39:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever go again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.80,1:39:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.54,1:39:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.53,1:39:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.53,1:39:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great. Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.69,1:40:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Being with you makes me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.78,1:40:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Drives me nuts!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.29,1:40:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.14,1:40:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are demented!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.39,1:40:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna be like your sister?\NWell you already are.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.65,1:40:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep around, get knocked up,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.28,1:40:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,spitting image of that sister you love!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.57,1:40:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.86,1:40:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.53,1:40:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.39,1:40:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.34,1:40:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.34,1:41:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.93,1:41:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.98,1:41:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you pulling the same,\N"Go away" crap on him?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.53,1:41:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.59,1:41:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister! Sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.48,1:41:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister used to say...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.12,1:41:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"My own sister scares me."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.48,1:41:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!\NDon't!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.70,1:41:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it always have to be\Nso damn dramatic?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.10,1:41:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. Give me back the ring, the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.46,1:41:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.59,1:41:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.24,1:41:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you\N"All I did for you" me!? {Man this entire section is messed up. I have zero idea what this even refers to}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.39,1:41:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You never did a thing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.89,1:41:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister did everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.91,1:41:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.94,1:41:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it with you!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.39,1:42:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.81,1:42:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out! You!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.69,1:42:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.64,1:42:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back the ring!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.18,1:42:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you callin' stupid?!\NWho doesn't get it?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.70,1:42:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.36,1:42:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.43,1:42:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.76,1:42:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.42,1:42:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my life!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.37,1:42:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.08,1:43:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, why were\Nyou with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.71,1:43:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.68,1:43:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After you disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.55,1:43:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,he came after me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.36,1:44:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to go away?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.90,1:44:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.45,1:44:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretended to like me,\Nbut you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.43,1:44:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So God punished you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.84,1:44:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.\NBe happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.60,1:44:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.87,1:46:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.69,1:47:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.\NBe happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.69,1:47:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.54,1:47:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.65,1:47:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.50,1:47:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.69,1:47:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.62,1:47:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.64,1:47:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.06,1:47:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true,\N'cause she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.02,1:48:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.57,1:48:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming to see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.54,1:48:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.46,1:48:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.29,1:48:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.58,1:48:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.27,1:48:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.33,1:48:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.96,1:48:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She calls you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.62,1:48:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you answer my phone?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.44,1:48:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep out of my business!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.95,1:48:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut it's what's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.88,1:48:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.18,1:48:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.38,1:48:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.90,1:48:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!\NYou go away, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.57,1:48:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.52,1:48:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not running!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.56,1:48:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You run away from everything\Nyou don't like, and wind up
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.40,1:49:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in your own little world.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.30,1:49:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.07,1:49:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You just deny anything you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.56,1:49:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.47,1:49:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you want everyone to go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.01,1:49:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NCut the crap! You depress me!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.68,1:49:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?\NI told you to go...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.33,1:49:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.28,1:49:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.37,1:49:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.26,1:49:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,like...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.42,1:50:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.36,1:50:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.93,1:50:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.\NI like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.85,1:50:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying just like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.87,1:50:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.19,1:50:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.40,1:50:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.84,1:50:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.81,1:50:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.04,1:50:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.52,1:50:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.12,1:51:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.37,1:51:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little, my mother cursed my father
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.20,1:51:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to drive him away.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.99,1:51:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's curse came to pass
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.69,1:51:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and my father left.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.65,1:51:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried hard
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.78,1:51:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep her from driving me away.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.05,1:51:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But she told me,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.53,1:51:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,even though she never told my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.82,1:51:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.88,1:51:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A red umbrella and red shoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.65,1:51:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother bought them for me\Nwhen we went shopping together.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.46,1:52:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The first things that weren't\Nmy sisters hand-me-downs.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.61,1:52:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They matched my mother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.37,1:52:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But my mother threw them away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.32,1:52:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She called them old.\NSaid she didn't need them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.44,1:52:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw that,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.50,1:52:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she'd do that to me one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.69,1:52:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of being alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.41,1:52:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm scared of mother, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.99,1:52:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I cursed everyone to drive them away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.36,1:52:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The curse will come to pass on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.27,1:52:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So my birthday always has to be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.36,1:52:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But mother didn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.61,1:52:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to kill her\Nin my head, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.38,1:53:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.61,1:53:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that I had to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.32,1:53:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I began dressing up.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.76,1:53:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.43,1:53:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,would bring my
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.01,1:53:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,new and happy life.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.79,1:53:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.55,1:53:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.12,1:53:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.16,1:53:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All we really know
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.81,1:53:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is that tomorrow we'll still be together.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.63,1:53:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.69,1:53:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to try to see your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.47,1:54:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.99,1:54:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.77,1:54:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.23,1:54:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.67,1:54:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.65,1:54:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own mother? Leaving you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.89,1:54:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.80,1:54:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I left you alone for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.72,1:54:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I leave you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.73,1:54:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When did your mother leave you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.50,1:54:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.83,1:54:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you always left me alone...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.81,1:55:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You only cared for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.56,1:55:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.03,1:55:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did her sister pass away?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.66,1:55:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she still alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.80,1:55:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We are apart, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.84,1:55:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She worries about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.73,1:55:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She called me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.41,1:56:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd been out of touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.11,1:56:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.85,1:56:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.77,1:56:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so busy thinking...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.61,1:56:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about myself, that maybe\NI didn't think about your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.84,1:56:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was difficult for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.65,1:56:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.29,1:56:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Always complaining, always getting angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.26,1:56:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I never did anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.61,1:56:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I only...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.86,1:56:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,thought about myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.73,1:57:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I couldn't really love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.42,1:57:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.49,1:57:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.65,1:57:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.06,1:57:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's selfish...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.85,1:57:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.96,1:57:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's selfish of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.84,1:57:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about when I was lonely?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.36,1:57:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What about all those\Nyears when I was alone?!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.95,1:57:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All those...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.86,1:57:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't have cared less\Nwhen I needed your love,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.63,1:58:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but now you're lonely,\Nyou come to get me!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.49,1:58:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.94,1:58:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What! After all this time,\Nnow you're lonely!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.19,1:58:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.36,1:58:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.62,1:58:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.28,1:58:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was lonely,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.79,1:58:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you just ignored me...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.22,1:58:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.16,1:58:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!\NI'm asking you, go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.51,1:58:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go... Just go...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.71,1:58:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go away, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.10,1:58:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.67,1:58:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.17,1:58:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.87,1:58:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NI'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.47,1:58:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once, won't you come home?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.29,1:59:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come home just once? Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.64,1:59:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.03,1:59:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come home...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.72,1:59:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.43,1:59:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.33,1:59:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up from your dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.39,1:59:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this part of your dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.82,1:59:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we still dreaming a dream?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.74,2:00:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is our reality...\NYour reality.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.10,2:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.80,2:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,will come, on the day
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.76,2:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you were born.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.60,2:01:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.90,2:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,please smile.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.11,2:01:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.03,2:02:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What day
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.34,2:02:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is that?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.81,2:02:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,December 7th.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.31,2:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My birthday.
Comment: 0,2:02:36.89,2:02:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,---------- Ending ----------
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.84,2:02:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The red hair I got from my mom
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.91,2:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Braided in two
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.93,2:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Swaying in the wind
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.62,2:02:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why, why, I still don't know
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.20,2:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calmly I stood up
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.28,2:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scissors in hand
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.59,2:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and cut off those braids
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.55,2:03:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a sunny day
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.04,2:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future had no meaning
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.19,2:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was helpless, had no words
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.51,2:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the scent of the way home
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.27,2:03:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was tender
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.24,2:03:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can live
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.39,2:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somebody was laughing
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.58,2:04:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a very sunny day
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.88,2:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With no more hair
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.58,2:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cut off my arms
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.96,2:04:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kept cutting until I could {added line}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.88,2:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It felt warm {added line}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.58,2:04:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dancing, with my bloody arms
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.34,2:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without you
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.18,2:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was nothing here
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.59,2:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but only the bright sun
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.52,2:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a very sunny day
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.96,2:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Couldn't even cry
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.17,2:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The land had no limit
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.47,2:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beauty surrounded me
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.43,2:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was singing
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.41,2:05:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a white dress
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.31,2:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The line of people far away
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.32,2:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could've cried with a rain like today
